data.description: Presenting a generously upgraded 2-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse with attached garage that redefines modern living. This residence seamlessly blends style and functionality, offering a lifestyle of unparalleled comfort and sophistication. Step into a thoughtfully designed interior where every detail reflects the careful attention given to enhancements. The open-concept main level showcases upgraded LVP and carpet flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere that extends throughout the home. Large windows bathe the rooms in natural light. The kitchen is a focal point of this residence, featuring top-of-the-line Maytag appliances, generous island, and custom backsplash. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or enjoy casual dining, this kitchen sets the stage for memorable culinary experiences. A conveniently located 1/2 bath just off the garage round out this level of the home. Each of the two bedrooms has its own private updated bath. The primary suite boasts a beautiful ensuite bathroom with modern fixtures with LVP flooring. The walk-in closet maximizes storage. The spare bath has updated fixtures and features LVP and a new vanity. This home also offers a private outdoor escape. The upgraded landscaping in the spacious yard provides a perfect backdrop for relaxation or outdoor entertaining. Imagine enjoying al fresco dinners or unwinding in your own sanctuary under the stars. Conveniently located providing easy access to local amenities, shopping, dining, entertainment, cultural attractions and quick access to Powers Blvd. Experience the epitome of refined living in this upgraded 2-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse. Schedule a showing today and witness firsthand the seamless fusion of contemporary design and elevated functionality. Notable recent upgrades: Tankless water heater, extra attic insulation in 2023. Sink, faucet, backsplash, counter tops and garbage disposal in 2022.
